    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've gotta see this beauty in person to believe it! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I've taken such good care of it, and it's been my absolute pride and joy, but it's time for it to find a new home. It's spotless inside and out, runs like a total dream, and is ready for its next adventure with you! Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look and fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
